  <section class="bg-[url(/images/share_y_instants_bg.webp)] bg-cover">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-lg px-4 grid grid-cols-12 gap-y-0 py-20">
      <Heading htmlheading="h3" size="small_dark" font="h3_dark" stylingclasses="col-start-3 col-span-7">Share your</Heading>
      <Heading htmlheading="h3" size="small_dark" font="h3_dark" stylingclasses="col-start-6 col-span-6 -mt-6">instants!</Heading>
      <Heading htmlheading="h4" size="xsmall" font="h4" stylingclasses="col-start-3 col-span-5 mt-10">How to participate? </Heading>
      <Text teksttype="Light" stylingclasses="col-start-3 col-span-9 pt-2 pb-7">So: Got an instant photo ready for the public? In order to take part in Instant Day: </Text>
  <Text teksttype="Light" stylingclasses="col-start-3 col-span-9 py-3">
  <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-2">
    <li>Take a photo of your instant with your smartphone (or scan it for max. quality) - the file should be between 2 - 10 MB, in jpg/jpeg or webp format.</li>
    <li>Upload your photo and credentials on [link til din “share your instants” side]</li>
    <li>Agree to our terms and conditions [link til din “terms and conditions” sektion på “share your instants” siden]...</li>
    <li>You can make up to 5 submissions - go through step 1-3 for each submission ;-)</li>
  </ol>
</Text>
</section>

